name: Persephone
description:
Transmutation series | ✨Illustration N ° 1 
watercolor and digital graphite.

⚡In the shadows of the day something slides, moves. Slowly, we abandon the skins, which fall lightly, worn by use. The light of a new day improvises a melody and we dance as we can, celebrating at every step, on the ashes of a time past that was never better.
